<h2 id="purpose" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#purpose"><span>Purpose</span></a></h2>
<p>The purpose of this cookbook is to serve as a collaborative space where developers can explore and understand the intricate details of <strong>Stone.js</strong>.
